msgctxt "1039	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I need to get three marten pelts and give them to the guy in the village."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1113	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The village's trader needs a million yen worth of business from what I hunt and trap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1199	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There are twelve Jizo statues on the mountain. I oughta pray to them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1269	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I should get bear meat and bring it to Kihachi-han."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1321	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Let's find that time capsule buried at the Ghost Pine for that grievin' guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1398	EXPLANATION"
msgid "A guy and his old mother went to the mountain. I should check on them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1469	EXPLANATION"
msgid "A woman wants some rabbit meat for her mother-in-law's meal. I oughta help her out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1553	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Let's find an antler for that guy with performance issues. Gotta help a brother out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1638	EXPLANATION"
msgid "This guy in the village wants me to hunt a gold stag. This better not be a wild goose chase."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1731	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta collect three toxic mushrooms for that fella from Tsukimino."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1798	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Let's get Okudera-han to check my shootin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1842	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There's a rumor of a wild snowman. How's a snowman runnin' around on its own?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1920	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Let's find some bear fat for the woman in the village who has skin trouble."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1996	EXPLANATION"
msgid "A trapper went up the mountain. I should stop and say hi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2054	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta find a bear skin for that guy who ruined a yakuza's bear skin rug."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2127	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The trader said he'd pay double for a marten pelt. If I get one, it's his."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2202	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The trader said he'd pay double for a fox skin. If I get one, it's his."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2274	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The trader said he'd pay double for deer meat. If I get some, it's his."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2346	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The trader said he'd pay double for a whole deer. If I get one, it's his."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2420	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The trader said he'd pay double for a whole bear. If I get one, it's his."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2494	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Got the three marten pelts to the guy in the village. Glad to see him happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2571	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Finally sold the village's trader a million yen worth of what I hunted and trapped."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2655	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "I visited all twelve Jizo statues on the mountain. Hope some good comes of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2734	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Got bear meat for Kihachi-han. Feels good to be appreciated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2795	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Found the time capsule buried at the Ghost Pine. Ya gotta cherish your parents."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2875	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Rescued the guy and his old mother from the mountain. Ya gotta respect the wild."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2956	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Got some rabbit meat for that woman. They're an interesting family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3024	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Found an antler for that deflated guy. Maybe it's worth a try."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3087	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Found a gold stag for the guy. Guess the legend was true."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3145	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "I got the three toxic mushrooms for that guy from Tsukimino. Medicine's an odd thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3231	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Looks like I passed Okudera-han's test. Gotta keep learnin', though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3300	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Turns out there was no wild snowman. It's fun to dream, I guess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3365	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Got the bear fat to the woman with bad skin. Marriage, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3425	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Rescued the trapper from his own trap. Can never be too careful, I guess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3499	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Found a bear skin for that ramen guy. That order sounded like a magic spell."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3576	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Sold a marten pelt to the trader."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3610	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Sold a fox skin to the trader."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3641	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Sold deer meat to the trader."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3671	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Sold a whole deer to the trader."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3704	EXPLANATION_END"
msgid "Sold a whole bear to the trader. Normal folks should steer clear of yakuza."
msgstr ""

